<%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>
<style>
    body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    text-align: center;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

p {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

ul li {
    margin: 10px 0;
}

ul li strong {
    font-weight: bold;
}

ul li a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #007bff;
}

ul li a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

form {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    background-color: #fff;
    text-align: left;
}

label {
    display: block;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

input[type="text"],
input[type="email"],
textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

button {
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
}

.height {
    min-height: 40vh;
}
 
</style>
<body>
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
        <p>Have questions, suggestions, or simply want to reach out? We'd love to hear from you! Feel free to get in touch with us through the following methods:</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:your.email@gmail.com">djudoeyop@gmail.com</a></li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+11234567890">+1 (123) 456-7890</a></li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> <a href="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Company+Name+Inc">DJUD6 & co.</a></li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Connect with us on social media:</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/DJUD6">Facebook</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://twitter.com/DJUD6">Twitter</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/DJUD6">LinkedIn</a></li>
        </ul>

        <form>
            <label for="name">Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
            
            <label for="email">Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            
            <label for="message">Message:</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
            
            <button>Submit</button>
        </form>
    
</body>
